{"tid":1622901,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"【清算彈藥】今日元朗14歲中足中槍 證明左兩件事！！！","createTime":"2019-10-04T17:35:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:14:51.000Z","uid":56751,"like":90,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"4b9c8ade57051c4d797f387ec102d9568223314a","tid":1622901,"uid":56751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:35:33.000Z","msg":"可能大家都覺得今次開槍嘅警察好難有位俾人入，因為佢係受到襲擊後開槍<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">但係 </span></strong></span>依家就將呢單野同10月1號果單「槍殺」比較，<br />\n *10月1警察係喺冇受傷*既情況下開槍，而今次係有受傷 <br />\n上次手足中嘅係心口，而今次手足中嘅係大腿<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">聰明既你會睇到兩樣野：<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第一</span></span></strong>，今次呢個便衣警員<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係受左傷先開槍，</span></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">正正反證到10月1個防暴警，喺冇受傷既情況下係唔應該、亦唔需要開槍</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">第二</span></span></strong>，警察應該<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有選擇同埋有能力</span></span></strong>，打佢心口以外嘅地方<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">所以10月1條廢柴係唔應該咁開槍，</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>黑警謀殺罪名成立！！！</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"6ec28e4e476f784dad25108105baa7d7f8e2b7af","tid":1622901,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:36:24.000Z","msg":"［極重要］做嘢還做嘢，P牌仔想畀個革命方向大家討論討論<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1621742\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1621742</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"bc9aa9ae471dd480b9196252ea4a0b43a7642c40","tid":1622901,"uid":86699,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T17:39: